Title: DONNA VEKIC CHASES PRE-PANDEMIC PEAK AS CITI OPEN RETURN KICKS OFF US OPEN CAMPAIGN
Content: The 2018 D.C. runner-up reached her first major quarterfinal three years ago in Flushing Meadows, and arrives in North America fresh off her first proper training bloc since struggling with a persistent right knee injury.
